Package org.codehaus.cargo.generic.configuration

Class DefaultConfigurationFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codehaus.cargo.util.log.LoggedObject
      • org.codehaus.cargo.generic.spi.AbstractGenericHintFactory<T>
        • org.codehaus.cargo.generic.spi.AbstractIntrospectionGenericHintFactory<Configuration>
          • org.codehaus.cargo.generic.configuration.DefaultConfigurationFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationFactory, Loggable
    public class DefaultConfigurationFactory
extends AbstractIntrospectionGenericHintFactory<Configuration>
implements ConfigurationFactory
    Default ConfigurationFactory implementation that has all the known container configurations registered against their containers. It also supports registering new configurations against any container.
